window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Tad Harrington successfully closed Warrior Titan, but at what cost?</b></p> <p>He lost friends, loved ones, and even himself. With no sign of his brother Liam, Tad must face his champion rank-up trial, gain strength, and save his brother alone.</p> <p>What of other loose ends? What of the mysterious void egg, or his new silver dagger, Agony? Worse yet, wearing the skin of his former enemy, how will it interfere with his relationships?</p>"; 
